{
  "stem": "2578.3",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And when this Russian soldier, the officer, spoke to us, he could more or less translate-- maybe not word for word, but at least more or less the general meaning of what he said.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "All I remember was that the Russian officer told us that the Russian army came in from, from deep Russia.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "They are now on the German territory.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And they are here, and we are free.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "We should remain calm.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "We should remain in places where we are-- that where we were-- not that we were able of doing anything or going someplace.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And the Russian army will come in soon.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "Of course, we all started to cry.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 13 SECONDS] Just a minute.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "No one-- no one of us believed that-- [SIGH] [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] that day will ever come.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, we, we realized that it is true.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But no one believed that, that we will live to see this day.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Let's put it this way.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they left.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And about two hours later, the Russian army moved through the camp-- not into the camp, but whoever was able, capable, of walking out, they walked out from the camp on the road, to greet the Russians.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And they moved, moved around-- you know, they moved by.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And they started to throw food at us, everything that they had.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And we started to accumulate food.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I don't know how and from where, I happened to manage to found a straw sack.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Some, some inmates had, like a, like a sack made of, of, from, from straw, like-- from a straw material.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And it was filled with straw for their heads.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
